NOTICE — Third-Party Attribution

This project is inspired by and based on the work of imTHAI:
https://github.com/imTHAI/adguardhome-unbound-redis

The default configuration files shipped in this add-on (AdGuardHome.yaml,
unbound.conf, cache.conf, dnssec.conf, forward-queries.conf, redis.conf, and
any future additions) are extracted dynamically from the upstream Docker image
at build time. These files contain standard configuration values for their
respective software components (AdGuard Home, Unbound, Redis) and are included
to maintain config-folder compatibility with the upstream Docker container.

All original add-on code (Dockerfile, S6 service scripts, nginx configuration,
CI/CD workflows, documentation) is authored by PedroCPereiraDev and licensed
under the MIT License above.
